hopobject.body: Who's calling? elimite 5 for head lice The Texans, who already were debating how long they would go with the struggling Schaub, now get to see what Keenum can do while Schaub recovers. Unfortunately, Keenum's debut comes in a brutal matchup with the Chiefs' defense in hostile Arrowhead Stadium. The Chiefs rank No. 3 in pass defense and are first in the NFL with 30 sacks (including 10 last week against Oakland) and are tied for first with 10 interceptions.
